curam.util.common.domain

Interface DomainNames.Core

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DomainNames.Root
    Enclosing interface:
    DomainNames

    public static interface DomainNames.Core
extends DomainNames.Root
    Core domain names are supported by the infrastructure, but they are not necessarily root domains. All root domains are also core domains.
